'''Jane Smitte''' is a patient who had an Evans Bypass.

==History==
Jane was in the hospital to have an Evans Bypass performed by [[Thomas Evans]] himself. She hadn't been able to take the stairs or play with her grandkids, which he said she'd be able to do after her surgery. Her surgery went very well.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She has two grandkids.
